lass\u003d\"p-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-xl text-primary mb-3\">独特外貌</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">大熊猫的黑白相间皮毛是其最显著特征。黑色部分包括耳朵、眼睛周围、四肢和肩部，其余部分为白色。</p> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>圆胖的身体和大头，比例与其他熊类不同</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>标志性的\"黑眼圈\"，可能有助于减少眩光</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>短而粗的尾巴，约10-15厘米长</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> <!-- 特征卡片 2 --> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-custom transform hover:-translate-y-2\"> <div class\u003d\"h-56 overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/1059/600/400\" alt\u003d\"熊猫食性\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-custom hover:scale-110\"> </div> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-xl text-primary mb-3\">特殊食性</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">尽管属于食肉目，大熊猫的饮食却几乎完全是竹子，每天消耗大量竹子以获取足够能量。</p> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>拥有特殊的伪拇指，帮助抓握竹子</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>强大的颌骨和扁平的臼齿，适合研磨坚韧的竹子</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>每天花费10-16小时进食，其余时间休息</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> <!-- 特征卡片 3 --> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-custom transform hover:-translate-y-2\"> <div class\u003d\"h-56 overflow-hidden\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/1058/600/400\" alt\u003d\"熊猫行为\" class\u003d\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-custom hover:scale-110\"> </div> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-xl text-primary mb-3\">行为习性</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">大熊猫通常独居，除繁殖季节外很少互动。它们性格温和，但也有很强的领地意识。</p> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-2 text-gray-600\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>擅长爬树和游泳，尽管体型笨重</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>通过气味标记和叫声进行交流</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check text-secondary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>每天睡眠10小时左右，通常在树杈或洞穴中</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 栖息地 --> <section id\u003d\"habitat\" class\u003d\"py-20 bg-white\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12\"> <div class\u003d\"lg:w-1/2 order-2 lg:order-1\"> <h2 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,3rem)] text-primary mb-6\">熊猫栖息地</h2> <div class\u003d\"w-24 h-1 bg-accent mb-8\"></div> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed\"> 大熊猫的自然栖息地主要位于中国中西部的山区，包括四川、陕西和甘肃省。这些地区海拔通常在1200-3500米之间，气候凉爽湿润，非常适合竹林生长。 </p> <div class\u003d\"space-y-6 mb-8\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-secondary/10 p-3 rounded-full mr-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-tree text-secondary text-xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h3 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-xl text-primary mb-2\">竹林环境</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">大熊猫栖息地以茂密的竹林为主，提供了充足的食物来源和隐蔽场所。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-secondary/10 p-3 rounded-full mr-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-map-marker text-secondary text-xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h3 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-xl text-primary mb-2\">地理分布</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">目前约有95%的野生大熊猫生活在四川省，其余分布在陕西和甘肃省。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-secondary/10 p-3 rounded-full mr-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-temperature-half text-secondary text-xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h3 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-xl text-primary mb-2\">气候条件</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">栖息地气候凉爽湿润，年平均气温在10-20°C之间，年降水量丰富。</p> </div> </div> </div> <a href\u003d\"#\" class\u003d\"inline-flex items-center text-accent font-semibold hover:underline\"> <span>查看熊猫保护区地图</span> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-arrow-right ml-2\"></i> </a> </div> <div class\u003d\"lg:w-1/2 order-1 lg:order-2\"> <div class\u003d\"relative\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/1057/800/600\" alt\u003d\"熊猫栖息地\" class\u003d\"w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-xl\"> <div class\u003d\"absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-xs\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center mb-2\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-info-circle text-accent text-xl mr-2\"></i> <h4 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-lg\">重要数据</h4> </div> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 text-sm\"> 截至2023年，中国已建立67个大熊猫自然保护区，覆盖了约60%的大熊猫栖息地。 </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 保护现状 --> <section id\u003d\"conservation\" class\u003d\"py-20 bg-secondary/5\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"> <div class\u003d\"text-center mb-16\"> <h2 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,3rem)] text-primary mb-4\">保护现状</h2> <div class\u003d\"w-24 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto mb-6\"></div> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">经过数十年的保护努力，大熊猫的生存状况得到显著改善，但仍面临诸多挑战</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center mb-6\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-green-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-line-chart text-green-600 text-2xl\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-2xl text-primary\">保护成果</h3> </div> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-4\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">2016年，大熊猫从\"濒危\"降级为\"易危\"物种</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">野生大熊猫数量从1980年代的约1114只增加到2023年的约1864只</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">建立了67个大熊猫自然保护区，保护面积超过3.3万平方公里</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">成功的圈养繁殖计划，全球圈养大熊猫数量超过600只</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">\"大熊猫国家公园\"的建立，整合保护区域，促进基因交流</span> </li> </ul> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg\"> <div class\u003d\"flex items-center mb-6\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-yellow-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-triangle text-yellow-600 text-2xl\"></i> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-2xl text-primary\">面临挑战</h3> </div> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-4\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">栖息地碎片化，阻碍熊猫种群间的基因交流</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">气候变化导致竹林分布变化，影响食物来源</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">野生熊猫繁殖率低，幼崽存活率面临挑战</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">人类活动干扰，包括旅游和基础设施建设</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-yellow-500 mt-1 mr-3\"></i> <span class\u003d\"text-gray-600\">疾病和自然灾害对野生种群构成威胁</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-primary text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl shadow-xl text-center\"> <h3 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4\">如何帮助保护大熊猫</h3> <p class\u003d\"max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8\">每个人都可以为大熊猫保护贡献力量，无论是通过支持保护组织、减少碳足迹，还是提高公众意识</p> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-heart text-accent text-3xl mb-4\"></i> <h4 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-lg mb-2\">支持保护组织</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-white/80 text-sm\">向专注于熊猫保护的组织捐款或成为会员</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-leaf text-accent text-3xl mb-4\"></i> <h4 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-lg mb-2\">环保生活方式</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-white/80 text-sm\">减少碳足迹，支持可持续产品，应对气候变化</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-comments text-accent text-3xl mb-4\"></i> <h4 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-lg mb-2\">传播 awareness</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-white/80 text-sm\">分享熊猫保护知识，提高公众保护意识</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-plane text-accent text-3xl mb-4\"></i> <h4 class\u003d\"font-semibold text-lg mb-2\">负责任旅游</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-white/80 text-sm\">选择对环境友好的旅游方式，参观正规保护区</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 图片库 --> <section id\u003d\"gallery\" class\u003d\"py-20 bg-white\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"> <div class\u003d\"text-center mb-16\"> <h2 class\u003d\"font-display font-bold text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,3rem)] text-primary mb-4\">熊猫图片库</h2> <div class\u003d\"w-24 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto mb-6\"></div> <p class\u003d\"text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">欣赏这些可爱的大熊猫照片，感受它们的魅力与可爱</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"> <div class\u003d\"gallery-item group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow